{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a570842f5c","title":"毛泽东会见法国总统蓬皮杜谈话节选","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f97336e4b5","index":0,"year":1973,"month":9,"day":12,"articleId":"a570842f5c"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jimi","name":"机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"epub","author":"宋永毅","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话.epub"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"jimi":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7c9cf76b8b","type":"paragraph","text":"1973年9月12日","index":0,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"b9e2bcf5bb","type":"paragraph","text":"【乔治•让•蓬皮杜(Georges Pompidou，1911-1974)，法国总理（1962～1968）和总统（任期1969年至1974年，于任内去世）。他是第一位访问中国的法国国家元首，也是西方国家元首访华第一人。】","index":1,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"f0562fb056","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（对蓬）我这个人文化不行，不懂外交。","index":2,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"85b6fbce8c","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：但是你很了解中国人民。","index":3,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"eabcf07095","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：了解一些，不完全了解。我年纪大了，搞了一些官僚主义。（对齐）也叫bureaucratism（官僚主义）吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"2b814a77ec","type":"paragraph","text":"齐：对，英文是bureaucratism（官僚主义）。","index":5,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"0bdae6421d","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：但是你过去也从事了很多活动。","index":6,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"79fe04070f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：哎呀，打了二十几年仗了，把精力也耗费得差不多。我是一个小学教员。","index":7,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"eed4d613b8","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：我也是教员。","index":8,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"842f729718","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他当过中学教员。","index":9,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"3aa73c0bbb","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我是primary school teacher（小学教员），形势把我逼去打仗。那么要打呢，就打吧。一打就是二十几年。后头还跟美国人在朝鲜打了一仗。跟蒋介石打得多了。跟日本人打了八年。所以外国人到中国，现在这个时代比较难。中国人打游击战争可以。（蓬笑）","index":10,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"67331e9ecd","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：我曾有机会见到这两个大国的领导人，他们宣布自己是爱好和平的。我认为他们有理由现在成为爱好和平的人。","index":11,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"2d467d39e0","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我不信。","index":12,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"},{"id":"02e6384cee","type":"paragraph","text":"战争总有一天是要打的。（蓬无可奈何地举手向天。）宁可放在这个“打”字上，把第二个才放在和平上——peace（和平），不然就要丧失警惕。<br style=\"clear:both;\">","index":13,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c"}],"page":{"id":"f1e9ebd2d7","publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"a570842f5c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}